WEBVTT

00:00:06.820 --> 00:00:08.620
=Destiny of the General's Bride=

00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:12.020
=Episode 17=

00:00:16.559 --> 00:00:17.239
Mother.

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:20.519
I've found Qing Yan's weakness.

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:23.320
Empress Dowager and Princess are here.

00:00:23.960 --> 00:00:25.440
If you keep raving,

00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:26.600
you'll lose your head.

00:00:28.440 --> 00:00:30.559
The one to lose a head won't be me.

00:00:31.559 --> 00:00:32.679
Ghosts demanding lives,

00:00:32.679 --> 00:00:33.880
Su Hua returning,

00:00:34.679 --> 00:00:35.880
these are all lies.

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:37.960
I've already uncovered the truth.

00:00:38.240 --> 00:00:39.600
It was Qing Yan's doing.

00:00:40.719 --> 00:00:42.600
She must have known Su Hua.

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:45.079
She only wants revenge.

00:00:46.280 --> 00:00:47.880
Empress Dowager and Princess are here.

00:00:48.359 --> 00:00:49.920
We must not let them succeed.

00:00:51.119 --> 00:00:53.479
Burn the old evidence at once.

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:55.359
Put someone to watch that servant.

00:00:55.479 --> 00:00:56.359
She must not

00:00:56.359 --> 00:00:58.079
tell Empress Dowager anything.

00:00:58.560 --> 00:01:01.159
Rest assured. I had everything ready.

00:01:01.640 --> 00:01:04.599
And I've found something else.

00:01:06.239 --> 00:01:07.719
Mother, look.

00:01:10.879 --> 00:01:11.879
I told you so.

00:01:12.239 --> 00:01:13.680
That house in An County?

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:15.120
That "authentic work" of Liu Shuzhen?

00:01:15.120 --> 00:01:17.000
No way Qing Yan could've afforded them.

00:01:17.599 --> 00:01:18.280
It turns out,

00:01:18.480 --> 00:01:20.599
it was never from An County at all.

00:01:21.159 --> 00:01:23.280
She just converted our shed room.

00:01:24.719 --> 00:01:25.760
Are you certain?

00:01:26.519 --> 00:01:27.280
See for yourself.

00:01:27.719 --> 00:01:28.920
The soil is old.

00:01:29.239 --> 00:01:30.719
No trace of being moved.

00:01:31.959 --> 00:01:33.280
Now I'm sure.

00:01:34.319 --> 00:01:35.200
This house

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:37.280
was never from An County.

00:01:41.879 --> 00:01:44.879
Since she knew Su Hua,

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:47.560
and sought revenge for her friend,

00:01:48.079 --> 00:01:50.079
we could give her a hand.

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:52.079
We'll reunite her

00:01:52.879 --> 00:01:54.519
with her dead friend.

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:04.680
Excellent.

00:02:05.239 --> 00:02:07.079
Another volume of
"Record by the West Window" recovered.

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:09.159
It can be passed down for generations.

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:11.000
When I return to the capital,

00:02:11.439 --> 00:02:13.240
I will tell His Majesty

00:02:13.479 --> 00:02:14.879
of your devotion.

00:02:15.479 --> 00:02:17.680
Moving a house here from An County

00:02:18.479 --> 00:02:19.719
is truly a remarkable feat.

00:02:25.039 --> 00:02:27.879
Your Highness,
we were deceived by the evil.

00:02:27.879 --> 00:02:29.680
We beg Your Highness's judgment.

00:02:30.039 --> 00:02:31.960
What is this? Speak on your feet.

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:33.719
I dare not rise.

00:02:34.159 --> 00:02:37.400
For Qing Yan has committed
the crime of treason.

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:41.080
I don't understand what she speaks of.

00:02:41.240 --> 00:02:42.680
Please make it clear.

00:02:43.319 --> 00:02:44.599
Speak plainly.

00:02:44.759 --> 00:02:46.560
What crime has Qing Yan committed?

00:02:47.240 --> 00:02:49.759
The moment I entered this place,
I knew it seemed familiar.

00:02:50.240 --> 00:02:52.520
It looked just like the shed
of the Xiao Residence.

00:02:52.840 --> 00:02:54.039
But Qing Yan claimed

00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:57.319
it was an old house from An County.

00:02:57.520 --> 00:02:59.479
I saw the writing on the wall.
They were old and faded.

00:02:59.479 --> 00:03:00.759
I believed her words.

00:03:00.960 --> 00:03:01.759
After all, this girl

00:03:01.759 --> 00:03:04.199
would never dare deceive
Her Highness herself.

00:03:04.639 --> 00:03:05.960
So I gave it no further thought.

00:03:06.439 --> 00:03:07.240
Until...

00:03:09.520 --> 00:03:11.479
Until Ye examined
the soil around the house,

00:03:11.759 --> 00:03:13.159
and found it was all old earth,

00:03:13.759 --> 00:03:15.400
with no sign of disturbance.

00:03:15.919 --> 00:03:17.560
Only then did I realize the truth.

00:03:17.759 --> 00:03:20.159
This little wench did the unthinkable.

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:21.759
There was never an old house

00:03:22.240 --> 00:03:23.840
or the authentic work of Liu Shuzhen.

00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:25.319
These were nothing but her lies.

00:03:25.719 --> 00:03:27.800
She made a fool of Your Highness

00:03:28.039 --> 00:03:29.719
by lodging you in our shed.

00:03:29.919 --> 00:03:31.280
If word of this spreads,

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:32.680
where will Your Highness's dignity be?

00:03:32.680 --> 00:03:34.199
What of the honor of the royal house?

00:03:35.240 --> 00:03:36.039
Qing Yan,

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:37.400
what do you say?

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:41.919
Your Highness, do not believe her.

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:42.719
This house

00:03:42.919 --> 00:03:44.520
was indeed brought here from An County.

00:03:44.759 --> 00:03:46.479
I know not what she is accusing me of.

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:48.560
Perhaps

00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:51.560
the Grand Madam thought
Your Highness favored this place,

00:03:51.759 --> 00:03:54.520
and accused me falsely
so I couldn't claim credit.

00:03:55.520 --> 00:03:57.879
Besides, if this were only
my family's shed,

00:03:58.879 --> 00:03:59.759
then why

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:02.960
would there be Liu Shuzhen's
"Record by the West Window" on the walls?

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:05.159
That is simple.

00:04:05.759 --> 00:04:08.120
You had men
cover the walls with yellow clay,

00:04:08.759 --> 00:04:10.840
then called in scholars of some skill

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:12.319
to forge the stories behind it.

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:13.319
It's easy to

00:04:13.639 --> 00:04:15.159
make the shed look old.

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:17.279
Your Highness,

00:04:17.759 --> 00:04:19.600
if you will have the clay stripped away,

00:04:19.759 --> 00:04:20.600
I can guarantee

00:04:20.879 --> 00:04:23.120
you will find fresh walls beneath.

00:04:24.439 --> 00:04:25.160
Qing Yan,

00:04:25.680 --> 00:04:27.759
this concerns the missing volumes
of "Record by the West Window".

00:04:27.759 --> 00:04:29.319
I must be absolutely certain.

00:04:29.319 --> 00:04:30.360
Tell me.

00:04:30.680 --> 00:04:33.399
Was this house brought from An County,

00:04:33.639 --> 00:04:35.639
or was it the Xiao family's shed?

00:04:35.639 --> 00:04:37.360
I want the truth.

00:04:37.839 --> 00:04:38.439
If not,

00:04:38.519 --> 00:04:40.319
I will punish you
by the law of the realm.

00:04:42.319 --> 00:04:43.160
Your Highness,

00:04:43.519 --> 00:04:44.160
this house

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:46.120
was indeed brought here from An County.

00:04:46.439 --> 00:04:47.480
If so,

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:50.560
then I will have the walls
torn down to prove it.

00:04:51.120 --> 00:04:53.800
Otherwise, if I am deceived,

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:56.720
how can I answer
to the scholars of the world?

00:04:56.839 --> 00:04:58.439
Men, tear down the walls.

00:04:58.720 --> 00:04:59.319
Your Highness!

00:05:00.720 --> 00:05:01.360
Allow me.

00:05:01.759 --> 00:05:02.560
Your Highness,

00:05:02.639 --> 00:05:03.759
this house must not be damaged.

00:05:03.759 --> 00:05:05.360
This truly is the work of Liu Shuzhen.

00:05:05.360 --> 00:05:06.160
If you destroy it,

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:07.480
it will be an unforgivable waste.

00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:08.360
Qing Yan,

00:05:09.040 --> 00:05:10.120
are you afraid?

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:12.959
My conscience is clear.

00:05:13.319 --> 00:05:14.319
What is there to fear?

00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:17.120
Then, we'll tear it down!

00:05:18.120 --> 00:05:19.560
If this is truly a shed,

00:05:20.439 --> 00:05:23.199
you could lose your head, Qing Yan.

00:05:40.160 --> 00:05:40.759
Your Highness.

00:05:41.279 --> 00:05:43.800
Beneath the old wall lies a new one.

00:05:44.519 --> 00:05:45.240
This house

00:05:45.439 --> 00:05:47.920
was never an old residence
from An County.

00:05:48.279 --> 00:05:49.199
It was always

00:05:50.399 --> 00:05:51.920
the Xiao family's shed.

00:05:53.079 --> 00:05:54.360
You have all seen it.

00:05:56.240 --> 00:05:57.560
I have seen it with my own eyes.

00:05:58.480 --> 00:05:59.600
But, Your Highness,

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:02.360
did you see it as well?

00:06:05.439 --> 00:06:07.560
You saw only
the surface of the new wall.

00:06:09.279 --> 00:06:10.800
But did you notice...

00:06:14.120 --> 00:06:15.920
the bloody handprints beneath it?

00:06:20.439 --> 00:06:22.120
And that is only the beginning.

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:25.279
Your Highness,

00:06:25.959 --> 00:06:28.480
please allow me to explain in full.

00:06:30.079 --> 00:06:30.879
This place

00:06:32.279 --> 00:06:35.480
is where Xiao Ye
violated countless women.

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:40.920
He not only defiled their honor,

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.800
but

00:06:43.519 --> 00:06:45.319
if they were not with child afterwards,

00:06:45.759 --> 00:06:47.720
he would poison them, making them mute

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:49.879
or blind,

00:06:53.480 --> 00:06:55.079
and cast them into the lake.

00:06:58.160 --> 00:07:01.000
So many women perished by his hand,

00:07:01.519 --> 00:07:02.879
with no place to seek justice.

00:07:04.079 --> 00:07:05.759
These bloody handprints are proof.

00:07:06.519 --> 00:07:08.920
The Xiao family is powerful
and has no regard

00:07:08.920 --> 00:07:10.120
for the law of the nation.

00:07:10.360 --> 00:07:11.800
Since I lived under their roof,

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:13.800
I could not speak openly.

00:07:14.639 --> 00:07:16.120
This was the only path left.

00:07:16.920 --> 00:07:18.560
I had to bring Your Highness here

00:07:19.439 --> 00:07:20.560
so you could witness it.

00:07:22.680 --> 00:07:24.279
I beg Your Highness's pardon.

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:25.759
You made a lot of claims.

00:07:26.360 --> 00:07:27.399
Where is the proof?

00:07:32.079 --> 00:07:32.839
These are

00:07:33.079 --> 00:07:35.399
the names of the women
violated by Xiao Ye.

00:07:35.920 --> 00:07:37.160
Each one on this list

00:07:37.639 --> 00:07:39.759
was linked to Xiao Ye,

00:07:39.879 --> 00:07:41.360
then vanished without a trace.

00:07:41.720 --> 00:07:43.120
Your Highness need only investigate.

00:07:44.439 --> 00:07:46.439
This booklet must be her forgery.

00:07:46.439 --> 00:07:47.199
A forgery!

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:48.920
Your Highness!

00:07:58.360 --> 00:08:01.160
I, Xiao Lian,
will testify for Lady Qing Yan.

00:08:03.160 --> 00:08:04.319
I, Yu Luofu,

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:06.000
will also testify for Lady Qing Yan.

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:10.240
Impossible! This cannot be!

00:08:11.079 --> 00:08:11.800
Your Highness!

00:08:12.079 --> 00:08:12.879
I did not do this.

00:08:13.079 --> 00:08:13.879
None of this was my doing!

00:08:13.879 --> 00:08:14.519
Not you?

00:08:14.680 --> 00:08:15.680
Then who else?

00:08:26.839 --> 00:08:29.519
Mother! Speak for me!

00:08:29.879 --> 00:08:30.759
You know the truth!

00:08:31.040 --> 00:08:31.839
These women

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:33.519
were never kept here.

00:08:34.840 --> 00:08:35.600
And those blood prints,

00:08:35.879 --> 00:08:36.480
those stains...

00:08:36.720 --> 00:08:38.360
I already scrubbed them away!

00:08:38.759 --> 00:08:39.799
They have no proof!

00:08:40.919 --> 00:08:42.200
They have no proof!

00:08:44.960 --> 00:08:46.360
Not kept here?

00:08:47.559 --> 00:08:48.799
Then, where were they kept,

00:08:49.679 --> 00:08:50.600
Second Master Xiao?

00:08:57.840 --> 00:09:00.000
Guards! Get Ye out of here.

00:09:00.519 --> 00:09:01.799
With a scandal this grave,

00:09:02.159 --> 00:09:04.879
does Madam Xiao
mean to confine him for trial,

00:09:05.120 --> 00:09:06.759
or to send him away in secret?

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:09.720
Mother! Save me!

00:09:10.279 --> 00:09:11.720
He will be confined first

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:13.799
to await your judgment.

00:09:19.519 --> 00:09:20.879
Your Highness, I beg you!

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:22.399
My son may be foolish,

00:09:22.720 --> 00:09:24.919
but Qing Yan is truly vicious.

00:09:25.159 --> 00:09:27.559
She already knew
the walls were stained with blood,

00:09:27.679 --> 00:09:29.279
yet still allowed you to lodge here,

00:09:29.279 --> 00:09:30.559
two nights!

00:09:30.679 --> 00:09:33.000
Then, she wove lies
to mislead Your Highness.

00:09:33.159 --> 00:09:34.240
Her intentions are vile.

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:35.200
She means to doom us!

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:36.200
Your Highness!

00:09:37.559 --> 00:09:38.200
Qing Yan,

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:39.679
what do you have to say?

00:09:40.559 --> 00:09:41.559
Your Highness,

00:09:42.559 --> 00:09:44.159
if you will examine this case,

00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:46.360
and bring justice to these women,

00:09:47.679 --> 00:09:49.159
then even if my action
costs me my life,

00:09:51.919 --> 00:09:53.240
I shall have peace in death.

00:09:57.360 --> 00:09:58.480
Take them all into custody.

00:10:17.759 --> 00:10:19.200
Qing Yan, oh Qing Yan.

00:10:19.840 --> 00:10:21.159
I warned you long ago

00:10:21.320 --> 00:10:22.919
that you cannot bring me down.

00:10:23.039 --> 00:10:24.960
The King of Xiling has my back.

00:10:26.159 --> 00:10:27.360
And who can save you now?

00:10:27.879 --> 00:10:28.919
By tomorrow,

00:10:29.320 --> 00:10:30.240
we shall see

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:33.200
which of us will end up dead.

00:10:35.320 --> 00:10:36.559
It will be you, of course.

00:10:40.759 --> 00:10:42.960
I have already presented
your crimes to the court.

00:10:43.159 --> 00:10:44.720
What of the King of Xiling?

00:10:45.240 --> 00:10:47.120
All under heaven belongs to Emperor.

00:10:47.639 --> 00:10:49.720
Does the King of Xiling dare defy him?

00:11:06.360 --> 00:11:07.799
Wasn't the plan going smoothly?

00:11:08.120 --> 00:11:09.360
Why are you so angry?

00:11:10.799 --> 00:11:11.600
Smoothly?

00:11:12.559 --> 00:11:14.559
Did you plan to
sacrifice yourself all along?

00:11:18.039 --> 00:11:20.679
I wanted you to see
that I have the strength

00:11:20.919 --> 00:11:21.759
to stand up

00:11:21.759 --> 00:11:23.480
for myself and those women.

00:11:23.679 --> 00:11:25.200
I protected myself, didn't I?

00:11:25.759 --> 00:11:26.960
Empress Dowager is furious

00:11:26.960 --> 00:11:28.080
because you used her.

00:11:28.159 --> 00:11:29.960
You stepped on a tiger's tail.

00:11:30.080 --> 00:11:31.919
Do you not fear she will take your life?

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:33.960
Xiao Lian said that

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:36.320
when Empress Dowager
read the words on the wall,

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:37.399
she was deeply moved.

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:39.799
She couldn't hold back her tears

00:11:39.840 --> 00:11:40.879
for the lady in the tale.

00:11:41.559 --> 00:11:43.399
There are so many victims like us.

00:11:43.559 --> 00:11:46.080
I believe she won't turn a blind eye.

00:11:46.759 --> 00:11:47.919
Empress Dowager's heart,

00:11:48.639 --> 00:11:51.600
like yours and mine,
still knows kindness.

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:54.799
But those in the palace
are hard to fathom.

00:11:55.919 --> 00:11:58.360
She may weep for a story in a book,

00:11:58.879 --> 00:12:00.159
but are you so certain

00:12:01.039 --> 00:12:02.399
that her heart won't turn cold

00:12:02.399 --> 00:12:03.679
after discovering the deception?

00:12:04.039 --> 00:12:05.240
But I succeeded.

00:12:05.519 --> 00:12:07.000
And if you had not?

00:12:07.799 --> 00:12:08.600
Hua...

00:12:09.039 --> 00:12:10.799
I already lost you once.

00:12:11.360 --> 00:12:12.879
If I were to lose you again,

00:12:14.320 --> 00:12:15.799
how would you have me endure it?

00:12:38.520 --> 00:12:42.240
♪Mountains and rivers rise and fall♪

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:45.440
♪The vast sea opens wide♪

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:49.440
♪Thank you for staying with me♪

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:53.520
♪To witness all the lights of the world♪

00:12:54.080 --> 00:12:58.280
♪I remember by the old tree in Qing Yan♪

00:12:58.880 --> 00:13:01.320
♪When we first met♪

00:13:01.960 --> 00:13:09.040
♪Looking back, no more words are needed♪

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:13.920
♪You went left, I went right♪

00:13:13.920 --> 00:13:18.000
♪If we hadn't met,
there'd be nothing to seek♪

00:13:18.680 --> 00:13:22.320
♪In this long, dusty road of life♪

00:13:22.320 --> 00:13:25.920
♪Love and hate poured
in a single jar of wine♪

00:13:25.920 --> 00:13:29.800
♪Whose heart does love truly claim♪

00:13:29.800 --> 00:13:34.120
♪Yet it yields to just one greeting♪

00:13:34.960 --> 00:13:38.320
♪Gentle longing flows into the river♪

00:13:38.320 --> 00:13:44.120
♪When dreams break,
we will guard each other still♪